    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税给全球经济的心脏带来了故意的震惊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-tariffs-send-deliberate-shock-to-heart-of-global-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提出了一波新的关税，这将使他们在一个多世纪以来的平均征收最高征收时，他在白宫玫瑰花园（Rose Rose Garden）的助手和支持者大笑。对于经济学家，市场和世界其他地方，几乎没有什么可庆祝的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-tariffs-send-deliberate-shock-to-heart-of-global-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 13:23:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着关税威胁的增长，加拿大贸易余额会倒转以赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/canada-s-trade-balance-flips-to-deficit-as-tariff-threats-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普政府关税的威胁和实施开始重新汇款全球交易流动，加拿大向其最大客户，美国以及其他国家的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/canada-s-trade-balance-flips-to-deficit-as-tariff-threats-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的总督支出斧头正在悬挂在技术库存上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/musk-s-doge-spending-axe-is-hanging-over-technology-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）努力削减1万亿美元的联邦支出为受虐的科技投资者增加了另一种风险，威胁要从已经不稳定的行业中获得数十亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/musk-s-doge-spending-axe-is-hanging-over-technology-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长抛弃民主党初选，寻求独立竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nyc-mayor-adams-to-seek-reelection-as-independent-politico-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四面楚歌的纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）将放弃民主党初选，并作为一个独立竞选，并为一场比赛增加了另一个转折，该比赛上个月被前任州长安德鲁·库莫（Andrew Cuomo）的入口颠覆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nyc-mayor-adams-to-seek-reelection-as-independent-politico-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普以世界上关税最高的关税袭击非洲王国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-targets-african-kingdom-with-highest-tariff-in-the-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对莱索托（Lesotho）的小型南部非洲山王国征收了50％的互惠关税，这是任何主权国家的最高征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-targets-african-kingdom-with-highest-tariff-in-the-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:54:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
